Schlith had a wide reputation among both lizardfolk and [[aarakocra]] inhabitants of Coliar as being the most knowledgeable expert on the topic of [[spelljamming]]. The truth was that he did not know the details of how spelljamming worked at all; it was all a black box to him. However, he was indeed exceptionally knowledgeable about all manner of other topics of interest to spacefarers—the locations of the best restaurants and pubs, rumors, quests, ''etc''. He always made sure that his whereabouts were publicly known so that he could offer his services.
